2) Instructions

I always wanted to make thos cool
signatures on my emails, so I decied
to develop my own Font Server using
the free font files available on the
Internet for the Figlet Server.

To run the script use 'perl test.pl'.
The script will prompt you for a text,
enter whatever string (try to keep it
under 10 chars).
Then type in the font of your choice:
standard, lean, bublhead, fuzzy, trek,
or bubble (the script will use 
standard as the defalt font).

3) Tips

Type 'perl test.pl > file.txt' if you
want to save the output as a text file,
and use it as a signature for your email.

